{"tid":130700,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(正能量)我綺禮推薦幾套輕鬆溫馨關於青年照顧幼女既漫畫","createTime":"2017-02-22T14:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T21:02:28.000Z","uid":6327,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d860d08ef54e8f8f63515ef8675174a08a8b388","tid":130700,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"呢套個loli係比較好動同埋心智最符合年紀<br />\n姐係onon99<br />\n故事講無啦啦要暫時照顧個細路女<br />\n比較貼地同好笑 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/222646_00c9948c2f67848bf6d01fbf931cc94d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F222646_00c9948c2f67848bf6d01fbf931cc94d.jpg&h=6774b90c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個同上面果套類近 <br />\n只不過係改為照顧親戚個單親女<br />\n唔同既係呢個係無口loli<br />\n重點係非常能幹 <br />\n被託管要求照顧loli既男主反被loli照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21O5019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21O5019.jpg&h=1518d14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正既重心黎啦 傳說中既小說改篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講係勇者既男主偶然係森林遇上父母均遇害既魔族loli<br />\n然後帶翻去照顧及教佢講人話..作為養父<br />\n而係生活過程中loli慢慢將男主當作異性看待<br />\n一個字 萌到核爆<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/223339_75a0f2bc1aab51b367d41de4dd1eac0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F223339_75a0f2bc1aab51b367d41de4dd1eac0c.jpg&h=b4ea7934&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01c8408c0f30988738daa4096901a6fe61c278d0","tid":130700,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"少女不十分都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b822ad9a1d2439055b10fcf0856014695cfb1c5","tid":130700,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"雖然好多人識,